{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/LightKin_About_Banner.png?t=1664978065\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dance among embers</strong> - fly, dodge and pickup embers of varying colors as you fly up though the smoke of a blazing bonfire!<br></li><li><strong>Never the same</strong> - the game is ever changing as everything gets generated on the beat. Behold the mesmerizing patterns they create!<br></li><li><strong>Discover the embers</strong> - some embers are dying to meet you as they try to take your light for themselves.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/SteamBannerGifs_Bursting.gif?t=1664978065\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Bursting</strong> - burst to release the stored embers in an explosion of colorful fireworks to rack up your score. Repel the embers around you and give yourself some time to breathe!<br></li><li><strong>Multiply at own risk</strong> - burn brighter by keeping the kin within to grow your power but with great power comes great responsibility!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/SteamBannerGifs_Everburning.gif?t=1664978065\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Everburning embers</strong> - gain a random powerup as you can shield yourself from harm or burst infinite to bring your score to new heights!<br></li><li><strong>Leaderboards</strong> - burn your mark to secure your spot on the leaderboard, beware as the whole world will try to come for your crown!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/SteamBannerGifs_Music.gif?t=1664978065\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Adaptive music</strong> - listen closely as the music adapts to what is happening on screen. If the drums kick in, you know